column18: Didn't find a way to close the window of a question after answering it. Thus, the window with all teh questions was small and harder to navigate

It was not completely clear to me, if I should mark multiple ocurences of the correct answer (e.g. name mentioned multiple times) or only one. Some feedback about any improvement / worsening of the system after providing my labels would have been helpful - it currently doesn't feel like i improved the system / did anything meaningful.

I didn't notice any real improvement of the system, maybe it would have been good to include interacting with the system and looking at performance metrics between training rounds as part of the practical task. From the interface, I didn't actually see anywhere I could/should do that, so it was hard to see if the system was actually improving.
